你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinancialCrisisData.fetch_unemployment_rates', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisData.fetch_unemployment_rates', 'description': 'This function fetches unemployment rates for specified years.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'years', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of years for which unemployment rates are requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'unemployment_rates', 'description': 'A list of unemployment rates for the specified years.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisData.get_industry_changes', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisData.get_industry_changes', 'description': 'This function retrieves employment changes in different industries during specified crisis years.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_years', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of crisis years for which industry changes are requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'industry_changes', 'description': 'A list of employment changes in different industries during the specified crisis years.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisData.analyze_graduate_employment', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisData.analyze_graduate_employment', 'description': 'This function analyzes employment opportunities and challenges for recent graduates during specified crisis years.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_years', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of crisis years for which graduate employment analysis is requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'graduate_employment_analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of employment opportunities and challenges for recent graduates during the specified crisis years.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisData.get_coping_strategies', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisData.get_coping_strategies', 'description': 'This function provides strategies to cope with employment challenges during financial crises.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisis_years', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of crisis years for which coping strategies are requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'coping_strategies', 'description': 'A list of strategies to cope with employment challenges during the specified financial crises.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinancialCrisisData.fetch_unemployment_rates` 并传入 `years`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinancialCrisisData.fetch_unemployment_rates",
    "args": "{'years': [2018, 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022]}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
